</div>
<div class="promo-text-box"> <i class=" icon-pencil-circled fa fa-4x icon-color-2"></i>
<h3><strong>Get Instant Answers</strong></h3>
<p> Lawyers from various domains will get back to you in a while.</p>
</div>
<div class="promo-text-box"> <i class="  icon-heart-2 fa fa-4x icon-color-3"></i>
<h3><strong>Search Queries Tag-wise and Rate.</strong></h3>
<p> Get all the categorised answers and rate the queries and answers</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
 
</div>
 
</div>
 

 
